                The ChatBot Application uses advanced AI technology to provide automated responses and interactions with users. You acknowledge that the responses provided by the ChatBot are generated based on pre-programmed algorithms and data, and may not always be accurate or reliable.
            </p>

            <h4>Data Collection and Privacy</h4>
            <p>
                We may collect personal information during your interaction with the ChatBot, including but not limited to your name, email address, and any other information you provide. We are committed to protecting your privacy and will handle your data in accordance with our privacy policy.
            </p>

            <h4>Intellectual Property</h4>
            <p>
                All content within this application, including text, logos, graphics, and code, is the property of the ChatBot Application and is protected by copyright law. You may not copy, modify, or distribute any content from the application without prior written permission.
            </p>

            <h4>Prohibited Use</h4>
            <p>
                You agree not to use the ChatBot for any unlawful or malicious activities, including but not limited to spamming, generating harmful content, or engaging in abusive behavior.
            </p>

            <h4>Limitation of Liability</h4>
            <p>
                The ChatBot Application is provided on an "as-is" basis. We do not guarantee the accuracy or reliability of the responses and are not liable for any damages resulting from the use of this application.
            </p>

            <h4>Changes to Terms</h4>
            <p>
                We reserve the right to update or modify these terms and conditions at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and it is your responsibility to review these terms periodically.
            </p>

            <h4>Contact Us</h4>
            <p>
                If you have any questions or concerns about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at support@apnaai.com.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row-last text-center">
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Accept Terms</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

